window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The continent is in chaos as one world-shaking event after another continues to rattle the foundations that the people have lived with for centuries. The flames of all-out war threaten everyone, and few people seem to want to stop it. Louella and Regan work tirelessly to protect their own slice of home from forces that want to bring ruin to everything around them.</p> <p>As secrets and truths come to light, will Regan's intellect and Louella's compassion be enough to lead their people through the troubled time?</p>"; 
